---
import PreviewLayout from '../../layouts/PreviewLayout.astro';
import ActionLinks from '../../components/ActionLinks.astro';
import HoursPanel from '../../components/HoursPanel.astro';
import AccessPanel from '../../components/AccessPanel.astro';
import CtaBand from '../../components/CtaBand.astro';
import PreviewPatternNav from '../../components/PreviewPatternNav.astro';
import exterior from '../../assets/images/Exterior_01.jpg';
---
<PreviewLayout title="Experimental Typography" theme="experimental-typography" description="Codex再作成版。必須情報を削らず表現の上限を見る実験案です。">
  <article class="codex-pattern pattern-experimental"><section class="experimental-hero"><div class="preview-container"><PreviewPatternNav /><div class="poster-grid"><div><span class="codex-kicker">Codex redesign / Experimental</span><h1 class="poster-title">ASK<br />BEFORE<br />VISIT.</h1><div class="poster-info"><p>実験案でも、電話・LINE・地図・営業時間・アクセスは削らない。</p></div></div><div class="codex-photo poster-photo"><img src={exterior.src} alt="りんごちゃん薬局の外観" /></div></div></div></section><section class="preview-section"><div class="preview-container poster-required"><div class="poster-block"><ActionLinks /></div><div class="poster-block"><HoursPanel /><AccessPanel /></div></div></section><section class="preview-section"><div class="preview-container"><CtaBand title="表現は強く、導線は迷わせない" text="採用前提ではなく、良い要素だけ本番候補へ取り込むための実験です。" /></div></section></article>
</PreviewLayout>
